---
name: Update OCSF OSINT context from FoxIO JA4+
description: |
  Periodically fetches the FoxIO JA4+ database, maps fingerprints to OCSF OSINT
  Inventory Info events, and updates the generic OCSF OSINT lookup-table
  context.
---

every 1h {
  foxio::fetch
}
foxio::ocsf::map
tenzir::osint::update_context
